            <p>Here is the rest of the world: the news crews, government authorities, scientists, zealots, gawkers, merchants, faith-dealers, and hedonists. It&rsquo;s a holy place and a media circus, a modern-day temple fused with the energy of a bacchanalian night market, and a site of contention.</p>
